# deepwork
- by cal_newport, about how you should focus hard when studying and remove as many distractions from your lifestyle.
- focus deeply
- 4.5 hours of hard thinking max a day for exceptional mental athletes
- prioritise relationships but limit social media (maybe don't delete all as may lose contact with friends)
- embrace bordem, boredom is healthy for the brain in healthy amounts.

- https://calnewport.com/

